Package is a set of external Modules.

npm : Node Packeage Manager 

npm install nconf  // nconf is a package (about environmental variable). You can find package in [node_modules Folder]

package.json is a file which have package List. You can make this file from 'npm init' command.

npm uninstall nconf // uninstall nconf
npm install nconf --save // add this to dependencies.

